m2mimud.command
Class StringIntCommand

java.lang.Object
  m2mimud.command.Command
      m2mimud.command.StringIntCommand

public class StringIntCommand
extends Command

The StringIntCommand is for commands which carry both a string and it value. an exampe of this would be the buy command, which contains the String id of the item and the int amount the person is buying.
